comments: Professor Truesdale is pretty funny and keeps the lectures pretty short. There were about 8 quizzes and a final on top of the scheduled labs. If you complete your lab book with the right answers they will really help you with the quizzes. DO NOT MISS CLASS as you will loose participation points.
Class is super early in the morning and he only teaches the second half of the course. A lot better than the teacher who teaches the first half but still has extremely hard tests.
